{"type":"message","id":"428ee170","parentId":"06ab086e","timestamp":"2026-03-09T13:46:12.362Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Execute your Session Startup sequence now - read the required files before responding to the user. Then greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning.\nCurrent time: Monday, March 9th, 2026 — 9:44 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-03-09 13:44 UTC"}],"timestamp":1773063972360}}
