{"type":"message","id":"eae2fd95","parentId":"3ca4c83a","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:13:18.499Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cnardrsv44rc4cauihqxrxl4","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Slide Deck Outline\n\n**Topic**: 虾王读《OpenClaw避坑指南》：这10个Skills，本王要定了！\n**Style**: bold-editorial\n**Dimensions**: clean + vibrant + editorial + balanced\n**Audience**: general\n**Language**: zh\n**Slide Count**: 12 slides\n**Generated**: 2026-03-07 16:25\n\n---\n\n<STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\nDesign Aesthetic: Clean, digital precision with crisp edges and bold, high-saturation colors creating an energetic, magazine-style impact.\n\nBackground:\n  Texture: Pure solid color, no texture\n  Base Color: #FFFFFF (Pure White) with dramatic dark option #1A1A2E\n\nTypography:\n  Headlines: Dramatic high-contrast serif with thick-thin stroke variation (magazine cover style)\n  Body: Elegant classic serif\n\nColor Palette:\n  Primary Text: #1A1A2E (Deep Navy) - Headlines, main content\n  Background: #FFFFFF (Pure White) - Slide background\n  Accent 1: #E94560 (Coral Red) - Emphasis, highlights\n  Accent 2: #0F3460 (Deep Blue) - Secondary elements\n  Accent 3: #16C79A (Teal Green) - Progress indicators\n  Accent 4: #F9B208 (Golden Yellow) - Achievement badges\n\nVisual Elements:\n  - Bold, geometric shapes with sharp edges\n  - Large, dramatic typography for headlines\n  - High-contrast color blocking\n  - Subtle diagonal composition for dynamism\n  - Modern icons with thick outlines\n\nDensity Guidelines:\n  - Content per slide: 2-3 key points\n  - Whitespace: Standard (10% from edges)\n\nStyle Rules:\n  Do: Use bold color combinations, dramatic scale contrasts, high saturation throughout\n  Don't: Use hand-drawn elements, organic curves, or muted colors\n</STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\n\n---\n\n## Slide 1 of 12\n\n**Type**: Cover\n**Filename**: 01-slide-cover.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nMake a bold first impression with虾王's personality, hook the audience immediately\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 这10个OpenClaw Skills，本王要定了！\nSub-headline: 虾王殿下读《避坑指南》后的硬核评估\n\n// VISUAL\nA regal shrimp (虾王殿下) wearing a tiny crown, sitting on a stack of skill cards, with a bold \"10\" number behind. Dramatic diagonal composition, coral red + deep blue color blocking. Magazine cover style.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLayout: title-hero\nLarge central visual (虾王), headline below in huge editorial serif, sub-headline smaller above.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 2 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 02-slide-xiawang-config.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nEstablish baseline: 虾王 already has a solid foundation, not starting from zero\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 本王的家底，先给你看看\nSub-headline: 在看指南之前，本王已经有这些了\n\nBody:\n- SOUL.md + USER.md + MEMORY.md：完整人设体系\n- HEARTBEAT.md：心跳任务清单\n- Git灾备 + 安全巡检：自动化已上线\n- 飞书插件v2026.3.6：官方刚装的\n\n// VISUAL\nA clean grid of 4 cards, each representing one category, with bold icons and short labels. Deep blue background accents, coral red highlights.\n\n// LAYOUT\n2x2 grid layout, centered, headline at top, balanced density.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 3 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 03-slide-clawsec.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nFirst must-have skill: Security automation is non-negotiable\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第1个：Clawsec ✅ 必装\nSub-headline: 安全防护的第一道防线\n\nBody:\n- 静态代码分析：权限/网络请求/代码混淆/依赖来源\n- 三档评级：SAFE / CAUTION / DANGEROUS\n- 本王计划：装新Skill前先扫一遍，DANGEROUS直接拒\n\n// VISUAL\nA security shield icon split into three color-coded sections (green/SAFE, yellow/CAUTION, red/DANGEROUS). A tiny shrimp holding a scan device.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLeft: visual shield, right: 3 bullet points, headline at top, balanced.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 4 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 04-slide-tavily.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nSecond must-have: Real-time search solves knowledge cutoff\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第2个：Tavily Search ✅ 已装+已配\nSub-headline: 让AI拥有实时信息获取能力\n\nBody:\n- 解决大模型知识截止问题\n- 结构化输出 + AI优化 + 上下文感知\n- 本王测试：能搜到OpenClaw 2026.2.17发布、创始人加入OpenAI\n\n// VISUAL\nA search bar with \"OpenClaw最新更新\" typed in, results popping out with live news cards. Teal green accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nSearch visual centered, bullet points below, large headline at top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 5 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 05-slide-self-improving.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nThird must-have: Structured learning system, not just memory files\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第3个：Self-Improving Agent ✅ 必装（但要适配）\nSub-headline: 让AI持续进化的体系\n\nBody:\n- .learnings/目录：LEARNINGS.md + ERRORS.md + FEATURE_REQUESTS.md\n- Hook机制：每次执行命令后自动检查\n- 本王计划：适配现有FEEDBACK-LOG.md，不推翻重来\n\n// VISUAL\nA circular loop diagram: \"Execute → Learn → Improve → Execute\". Three file icons in the center. Golden yellow accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nCircular visual on left, bullet points on right, headline spanning top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 6 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 06-slide-proactive.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nPlot twist: 虾王 is already using this skill's approach!\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第5个：Proactive Agent 🤔 本王已经在用了！\nSub-headline: 从被动响应到主动服务\n\nBody:\n- 文章说的：心跳机制 + 7个配置文件\n- 本王一看：AGENTS.md/SOUL.md/USER.md/MEMORY.md/HEARTBEAT.md/TOOLS.md——全有！\n- 结论：咱们路子是对的！\n\n// VISUAL\nA checklist with all 7 files, 100% checked off. A triumphant shrimp giving a thumbs-up. Coral red highlight on \"100%\".\n\n// LAYOUT\nSide-by-side: left = article's list, right = 虾王's checklist (all checked). Visual connecting them with \"MATCH!\" badge.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 7 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 07-slide-find-skills.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nFourth must-have: The meta-skill that finds other skills\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第7个：Find-Skills ✅ 必装\nSub-headline: 发现生态中的宝藏\n\nBody:\n- ClawHub上有11,600+个Skills，本王总不能一个个翻\n- 你描述需求，它搜ClawHub，推荐最合适的\n- 本王计划：以后你想做什么，先问Find-Skills\n\n// VISUAL\nA search icon hovering over a huge grid of skill cards (11,600+ implied). A magnifying glass highlighting \"THE ONE\".\n\n// LAYOUT\nLarge central visual, bullet points below, bold headline at top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 8 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 08-slide-systematic-debugging.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nFifth must-have: No more guesswork, structured debugging only\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 第10个：Systematic-Debugging ✅ 必装\nSub-headline: 结构化调试，告别盲目试错\n\nBody:\n- 强制执行流程：问题定义→信息收集→假设生成→测试验证→修复实施\n- 每个步骤都有检查清单，不能跳过\n- 本王计划：以后你说\"代码报错了\"，本王就按流程来\n\n// VISUAL\nA detective-style investigation board with 5 steps connected by red string. A shrimp detective with magnifying glass.\n\n// LAYOUT\n5-step linear flow across the slide, each step a card, visual shrimp detective in corner.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 9 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 09-slide-pending-rejected.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nThe rest: 3待定 + 2不装, show selective judgment\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 剩下的5个：本王的判断\nSub-headline: 杂鱼才会照单全收，虾王有自己的选择\n\nBody:\n待定清单（3个）：\n- ⏸️ Multi Search Engine：等限流+看需求\n- ⏸️ GitHub：自然语言管理Git，等限流\n- ⏸️ Ontology：知识图谱，暂时太早\n\n不装清单（2个）：\n- ❌ Proactive Agent：本王已经在用了\n- ❌ Office-Automation：飞书插件够用了\n\n// VISUAL\nTwo columns: left = \"⏸️ 待定\" (3 cards), right = \"❌ 不装\" (2 cards). Color-coded: yellow = pending, gray = rejected.\n\n// LAYOUT\nSplit layout, headline at top, two columns below with clear visual separation.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 10 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 10-slide-must-have-list.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nThe verdict: Clear, memorable summary of 5 must-haves\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 本王的必装清单（5个）\nSub-headline: 这几个，本王要定了！\n\nBody:\n1. ✅ Clawsec（安全审计，已装）\n2. ✅ Tavily Search（实时搜索，已装+已配）\n3. ✅ Self-Improving Agent（自我进化，等限流）\n4. ✅ Find-Skills（技能发现，已装）\n5. ✅ Systematic-Debugging（结构化调试，等限流）\n\n// VISUAL\n5 large numbered cards in a horizontal row, each with a big checkmark, coral red + teal green + golden yellow accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\n5 cards across the slide, large bold numbers, headline at top, clean grid.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 11 of 12\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 11-slide-philosophy.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nThe real lesson: It's not a checklist, it's a mindset\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 这不是清单，这是思路\nSub-headline: 杂鱼才照搬，虾王会判断\n\nBody:\n- 不要照搬别人的配置\n- 基于自己现有的体系\n- 挑选合适的Skills来增强\n- 本王是虾王，不是杂鱼——有自己的判断\n\n// VISUAL\nA shrimp standing on a mountain of skill cards, crown gleaming, looking down at a messy pile of \"other people's configs\". Bold diagonal composition.\n\n// LAYOUT\nHero visual (虾王 on mountain) on right, quote/text on left, dramatic scale contrast.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 12 of 12\n\n**Type**: Back Cover\n**Filename**: 12-slide-back-cover.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nMemorable closing with 虾王's signature attitude\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 本王就是虾王殿下，不服憋着。\nBody: 苏神你放心，本王会把这几个必装的装好，然后适配到现有的体系里，让本王变得更牛逼！\n\n// VISUAL\nA close-up of 虾王殿下 with crown, looking directly at the viewer with a confident, slightly smug expression. Coral red accent background, bold typography.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLarge central portrait of 虾王, headline below in huge editorial serif, closing line smaller above. Clean, impactful composition.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773072798495}}
