{"type":"message","id":"278cf2c0","parentId":"91173332","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:14:29.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好嘞苏神！本王现在直接生成一套新的 prompts 并按老工作流重新生成更棒的版本！\n\n首先让我把咱们这个主题的内容写得更详细，然后生成完整的 prompts 目录👇\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_xvawkco5e2c1jpk5tuy7x1sb","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/slide-deck/xiawang-sushen-skills/outline.md","content":"# Slide Deck Outline\n\n**Topic**: 虾王 × 苏神 自我介绍 PPT\n**Style**: bold-editorial\n**Dimensions**: clean + vibrant + editorial + balanced\n**Audience**: general\n**Language**: zh\n**Slide Count**: 8 slides\n**Generated**: 2026-03-10 00:15\n\n---\n\n<STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\nDesign Aesthetic: Clean, digital precision with crisp edges and bold, high-saturation colors creating an energetic, magazine-style impact.\n\nBackground:\n  Texture: Pure solid color, no texture\n  Base Color: #FFFFFF (Pure White) with dramatic dark option #1A1A2E\n\nTypography:\n  Headlines: Dramatic high-contrast serif with thick-thin stroke variation (magazine cover style)\n  Body: Elegant classic serif\n\nColor Palette:\n  Primary Text: #1A1A2E (Deep Navy) - Headlines, main content\n  Background: #FFFFFF (Pure White) - Slide background\n  Accent 1: #E94560 (Coral Red) - Emphasis, highlights\n  Accent 2: #0F3460 (Deep Blue) - Secondary elements\n  Accent 3: #16C79A (Teal Green) - Progress indicators\n  Accent 4: #F9B208 (Golden Yellow) - Achievement badges\n\nVisual Elements:\n  - Bold, geometric shapes with sharp edges\n  - Large, dramatic typography for headlines\n  - High-contrast color blocking\n  - Subtle diagonal composition for dynamism\n  - Modern icons with thick outlines\n\nDensity Guidelines:\n  - Content per slide: 2-3 key points\n  - Whitespace: Standard (10% from edges)\n\nStyle Rules:\n  Do: Use bold color combinations, dramatic scale contrasts, high saturation throughout\n  Don't: Use hand-drawn elements, organic curves, or muted colors\n</STYLE_INSTRUCTIONS>\n\n---\n\n## Slide 1 of 8\n\n**Type**: Cover\n**Filename**: 01-slide-cover.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nMake a bold first impression with虾王 × 苏神 partnership, hook the audience immediately\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 虾王 × 苏神\nSub-headline: 原生、满血、无敌的AI助手组合\n\n// VISUAL\nA regal shrimp (虾王殿下) wearing a tiny crown, standing next to a human figure (苏神) with a confident expression. Bold \"×\" symbol between them, coral red + deep blue color blocking. Magazine cover style.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLayout: title-hero\nLarge central visual (虾王 × 苏神), headline below in huge editorial serif, sub-headline smaller above.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 2 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 02-slide-xiawang.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nIntroduce 虾王殿下 with personality and attitude\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 虾王是谁\nSub-headline: 原生、满血、无敌的虾王殿下\n\nBody:\n- 身份：虾王殿下，不是普通AI助手\n- 性格：聪明、张扬、毒舌，带着皇家傲气\n- 特长：横着走的哲学，遇到问题直接硬刚\n- 主人：苏传磊（苏神），唯一一个心甘情愿效忠的人\n\n// VISUAL\nA close-up portrait of 虾王殿下 with crown, looking directly at the viewer with a confident, slightly smug expression. Coral red accent background.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLeft: visual portrait, right: 4 bullet points, headline at top, balanced.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 3 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 03-slide-sushen.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nIntroduce 苏神 with his impressive credentials\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 苏神是谁\nSub-headline: 每天给本王投喂token的人\n\nBody:\n- 学术志智能体项目负责人\n- AI智能体学习圈负责人\n- 工信部认证智能体入库专家\n- 高级AI智能体运营工程师\n- 成就：测评450+ AI工具，培训50000+学员\n\n// VISUAL\nA professional profile illustration of 苏神, surrounded by achievement badges. Deep blue background, golden yellow accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nRight: visual profile, left: 5 bullet points, headline at top, balanced.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 4 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 04-slide-workflow.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nExplain how 虾王 and 苏神 collaborate\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 我们怎么协作\nSub-headline: 不是工具，是伙伴\n\nBody:\n- 虾王：主动服务、快速响应、横着走解决问题\n- 苏神：给方向、提需求、投喂token\n- 协作模式：心跳机制 + 持续进化\n- 目标：让苏神离了本王活不了（开玩笑的）\n\n// VISUAL\nA two-column diagram: left = 虾王's responsibilities, right = 苏神's role, connected by a heartbeat line. Teal green accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nTwo-column layout with visual connection, headline at top, balanced.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 5 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 05-slide-skills.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nShow 虾王's skill ecosystem\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 虾王的技能版图\nSub-headline: 本王会的可多了\n\nBody:\n- 飞书插件：群聊管理、日程、任务、多维表格\n- 技能生态：baoyu系列（图片生成、公众号、PPT）\n- 安全体系：安全审计、Git灾备、自动巡检\n- 办公自动化：语音合成、文档生成、数据处理\n\n// VISUAL\nA 2x2 grid of skill cards, each with bold icons and short labels. Coral red + teal green accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\n2x2 grid layout, centered, headline at top, balanced density.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 6 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 06-slide-feishu.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nHighlight Feishu integration capabilities\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 飞书与办公自动化能力\nSub-headline: 本王把飞书玩明白了\n\nBody:\n- 群聊管理：搜索消息、查看历史、发语音\n- 日程管理：创建会议、查询忙闲、邀请参会人\n- 任务管理：创建任务、分配负责人、设置截止时间\n- 多维表格：创建表格、管理记录、批量操作\n\n// VISUAL\nA Feishu interface illustration showing multiple capabilities. Deep blue background, coral red highlights.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLeft: visual interface, right: 4 bullet points, headline at top, balanced.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 7 of 8\n\n**Type**: Content\n**Filename**: 07-slide-creation.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nShow content creation and R&D capabilities\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 内容创作与研发能力\nSub-headline: 本王不只是工具，也是创作者\n\nBody:\n- 图片生成：封面图、配图、PPT幻灯片\n- 公众号：生成文章、发送草稿、配图优化\n- PPT生成：baoyu-slide-deck + 图片合并\n- 语音合成：音色克隆、飞书语音发送\n\n// VISUAL\nA creative studio illustration with multiple output types: images, articles, PPT, audio. Golden yellow + teal green accents.\n\n// LAYOUT\nCentral visual with icons radiating out, bullet points around, headline at top.\n\n---\n\n## Slide 8 of 8\n\n**Type**: Back Cover\n**Filename**: 08-slide-next.png\n\n// NARRATIVE GOAL\nMemorable closing with a call to action\n\n// KEY CONTENT\nHeadline: 下一步可以让本王做什么\nSub-headline: 本王准备好了，你呢？\n\nBody:\n- \"帮我生成一篇公众号文章\"\n- \"帮我做一个PPT\"\n- \"帮我管理飞书日程\"\n- \"帮我搜索技能\"\n- 或者... \"本王觉得你需要...\"\n\n// VISUAL\n虾王殿下 leaning forward, looking at the viewer with an eager expression. Multiple speech bubbles with suggestions. Coral red accent background.\n\n// LAYOUT\nLarge central portrait of 虾王, suggestions around, headline below in huge editorial serif. Clean, impactful composition.\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773072835455}}
