{"type":"message","id":"9a07b9ac","parentId":"e6a41da1","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:46:33.998Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[media attached: /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/645153fb-52de-41ac-9f43-66e5f29b0538.jpg (image/jpeg) | /Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/645153fb-52de-41ac-9f43-66e5f29b0538.jpg]\nTo send an image back, prefer the message tool (media/path/filePath). If you must inline, use MEDIA:https://example.com/image.jpg (spaces ok, quote if needed) or a safe relative path like MEDIA:./image.jpg. Avoid absolute paths (MEDIA:/...) and ~ paths — they are blocked for security. Keep caption in the text body.\nSystem: [2026-03-10 00:46:31 GMT+8] Feishu[default] DM | ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f [msg:om_x100b55dbd8aff8b4b33902d2ed2d7f5, image, 1 attachment(s)]\n\nConversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55dbd8aff8b4b33902d2ed2d7f5\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 00:46 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_0eb8fd7529b5669c0a2de183a76a760f\"\n}\n```\n\n/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/media/inbound/645153fb-52de-41ac-9f43-66e5f29b0538.jpg"}],"timestamp":1773074793992}}
