{"type":"message","id":"411f981d","parentId":"bdccc3f8","timestamp":"2026-03-09T16:56:36.046Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"好嘞苏神！本王立刻写今天的日记！\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d8vixz5dlknennxwzx48253q","name":"write","arguments":{"file_path":"/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-10.md","content":"# 2026-03-10 虾王日记\n\n## 📌 今日成就\n\n### PPT重新生成\n- **主题**：虾王 × 苏神 自我介绍 PPT\n- **版本**：v2.0（图片版）\n- **页数**：8页\n- **风格**：bold-editorial（clean + vibrant + editorial + balanced）\n- **生成流程**：\n  1. outline.md：重新编写8页大纲\n  2. prompts/：逐个生成8个详细提示词\n  3. DashScope生成图片（2048x1152）\n  4. sips压缩PNG→JPG（质量60）\n  5. merge-to-pptx.ts合并成PPT\n  6. send-feishu-file.sh发送给苏神\n- **结果**：从24.8MB压缩到2.3MB，成功发送飞书\n\n### 飞书文件发送能力修复\n- **问题**：之前忘记怎么用飞书机器人发文件了\n- **错误尝试**：message 工具 sendAttachment 一直报 validation error\n- **正确方式**：\n  1. 写了 `scripts/send-feishu-file.sh`（和 send-feishu-voice.sh 类似）\n  2. 用飞书应用身份先上传文件\n  3. 再发 msg_type=file 消息\n- **脚本位置**：`/Users/suchuanlei/.openclaw/workspace/scripts/send-feishu-file.sh`\n- **使用方法**：`scripts/send-feishu-file.sh /path/to/file --open-id ou_xxx` 或 `--chat-id oc_xxx`\n\n### 前两页重新生成\n- **第一页（封面）**：加入苏神形象描述（自信人类男性，短黑发，戴眼镜，温暖友好的表情）\n- **第二页（虾王是谁）**：加入虾王详细描述（威风凛凛的龙虾，精致小王冠，自信带点傲娇的眼神，钳子微微举起）\n- **生成方式**：DashScope（不能参考图片，只能用文字描述）\n- **结果**：用户满意，已发送最终版 PPT\n\n---\n\n## 📌 今日新增记忆\n\n### 飞书文件发送复盘（2026-03-10）\n已补充到 FEEDBACK-LOG.md：\n- 脚本：`send-feishu-file.sh`\n- 流程：app_id/app_secret → tenant_access_token → 上传文件 → 发 file 消息\n- 一次纠正永不再犯！\n\n---\n\n## 📌 待处理\n- 无\n\n---\n\n_本王今天真的长记性了！下次发文件绝对不会再忘！🦐_\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"ark-code-latest","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773075366733}}
